description: Python package and dependency management
globs: ["**/*.py", "**/*.pyw", "**/*.pyi", "**/pyproject.toml", "**/setup.py", "**/setup.cfg", "**/requirements.txt"]
alwaysApply: true
---

*UV*
- Use uv instead of pip. 
  - don't use requirements.txt
  - do use `pyproject.toml`
  - use `uv add [package]` or `uv remove [package]` as opposed editing `pyproject.toml` directly
  - always create a virtual environment under  `[root]\.venv` 
